href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Cover_Page#Animal_Theater\" title=\"Cover Page\">Animal Theater</a>: Agent <a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a>, carrying a case of Top Secret material, exchanges sign and countersign with the boatman at the closest <a href=\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E9%B6%B4#Japanese\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wiktionary:鶴\">Tsuru</a> Transportation stop.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While trying to save his friends, <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> falls into <a href=\"/wiki/Marianne\" title=\"Marianne\">Miss Goldenweek</a>'s <i>Colors Trap</i>. She is able to use the power of color to influence people's behavior and Luffy, being so simple-minded, is very easily influenced.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a> are chased by <a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a>. They are hit by Mr. 5's new weapon (using his breath to fire faster bullets), but Usopp is able to fire a Kaen Boshi to hit Luffy so that he can get rid of Miss Goldenweek's marks.\n</p><p><a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Vivi</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> get completely covered with wax.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Nami asks Luffy to free them from the candle, but Luffy seems unwilling to help even thought he realizes the danger.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, Usopp and Karoo are hiding in bushes and are suddenly found by Mr. 5 and Miss. Valentine. They explain that Luffy is under the spell of <i>Color Trap</i>, where she can influence the behavior of a victim based on the colors she draws on them, before attacking the duo. Usopp and Karoo try to escape, while Vivi realizes that Luffy's lethargic attitude must be due to of Miss Goldenweek, who explains her \"color trap\" ability.\n</p><p>Vivi then tricks Luffy into stepping out of the trap which returns Luffy to normal. Unfortunately, he then gets caught in another of Miss. Goldenweek's traps as she paints it directly on his shirt.\n</p><p>Nami, Zoro and Vivi look on in horror of their impeding doom.\n</p><p>Meanwhile, Mr. 5 and Miss Valentine are still chasing Usopp and Karoo, who frees Luffy from his trap but he is once again unable to combat Miss Goldenweeks' abilities. As the fight between the two duos continue, Mr. 5 realizes that he is not fast enough to catch Usopp and Karoo, while Usopp heads back to the candle and finds he friends waxed. Mr. 5 reveals a new weapon: a .44 revolver that can shoot 6 bullets at the same time.\n</p><p>However, instead of trying to help himself, Usopp fires at Luffy destroying his shirt and freeing him from color trap once more. Usopp is promptly shot by Mr. 5. Luffy becomes furious and declares that he will defeat them.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Marianne\" title=\"Marianne\">Miss Goldenweek</a>'s Colors Trap is introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> is hypnotized by the Colors Trap.</li>\n<li>Despite <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>, as well as Usopp's unintentional help Luffy gets re-hypnotized.</li>\n<li>Usopp realizes that Miss Goldenweek is responsible for Luffy's new behavior.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a>, having had enough of chasing Usopp and <a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a> with <a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a>, unveils his greatest weapon the Breeze Breath Bomb allowing him to overpower Usopp.</li>\n<li>Usopp succeeds in burning Luffy's shirt to free him from Miss Goldenweek's influence completely.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a>, Nami, <a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Vivi</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a> are completely covered in Mr. 3's wax.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Baroque Works</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> <i>(cover)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Little_Garden\" title=\"Little Garden\">Little Garden</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Brogy\" title=\"Brogy\">Brogy</a> <i>(petrified)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Dorry\" title=\"Dorry\">Dorry</a> <i>(K.O.)</i></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arabasta\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Arabasta\">Arabasta</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nefertari_Vivi\" title=\"Nefertari Vivi\">Nefertari Vivi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Karoo\" title=\"Karoo\">Karoo</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Baroque_Works#Members\" title=\"Baroque Works\">Officer Agents</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Marianne\" title=\"Marianne\">Miss Goldenweek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Gem\" title=\"Gem\">Mr. 5</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Mikita\" title=\"Mikita\">Miss Valentine</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_124%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nI went to one of the anime's wrap parties. The <i>One Piece</i> anime is entirely made possible by the remarkable people standing behind it.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\nアニメの打ち入りに行ってきた。本当に素晴らしい人達に支えられてアニメワンピースはできてる</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text